                                    in the course.
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-center align-middle">
                                <div> Lec: 3 units</div> 
                                <div> Lab: 0 unit</div>
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-center align-middle">
                                <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-warning">In-Active</span>
                            </td>
